In applications it's often useful to have tasks that run at scheduled times. Although not
quite as robust with regard to persistence of scheduled jobs, you could compare Polling Jobs
to Quartz.NET. With Polling Jobs in FubuTransportation however, your jobs run inside
a behavior chain in the same way your message handlers do.

